  "method": [
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Heat your oven to 200°C."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Drain your chickpeas, then pat them dry with a kitchen towel. Pour them onto a baking tray, and season them with half of the garam masala, as well as a drizzle of olive oil and a big pinch of salt. Toss the chickpeas so that they are evenly coated, then bake them for 30 mins until crispy."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Whilst your chickpeas cook, prep the rest. Add the coriander, green chilli, garlic clove, lime juice, half of the yoghurt, and ½ tsp salt. Whizz it up into a smooth green sauce. Taste and season with more salt, or lime if needed."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pour the green sauce into the remaining yoghurt, and stir together (this is so it doesn’t get too thin)."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pour 1/3 of this sauce into a bowl. Bash your chicken until 1cm thick, then add to the sauce, along with your remaining garam masala, and give it a good mix. Place onto a baking tray lined with baking paper and slide into the oven until fully cooked, 15-20 mins."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Once your chickpeas are cooked, set them aside to cool a bit."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Peel and finely chop your red onion. Halve your cherry tomatoes. Add your red onion to the large bowl with a pinch of salt."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pull your kale leaves off their stalks, and add the leaves to the onions. Drizzle with some olive oil, then massage your kale leaves, until the it looks a wet, dark green and has wilted."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Toss your cherry tomatoes and pomegranate seeds into the kale, and pour in your remaining green sauce. Give it a good toss so that the leaves are all coated, then add your chickpeas and briefly toss it again."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Spoon your salad into bowls, slice the chicken and serve it on top."
    }
  ],
